      <p>In the assessment of Mendelian Discordance Rate (MDR), we used Jasmine (<ext-link xlink:href="https://github.com/mkirsche/Jasmine" ext-link-type="uri">https://github.com/mkirsche/Jasmine</ext-link>) v1.1.1 to integrate the SV results produced by each SV caller on the GIAB Ashkenazi trio [<xref rid="ref43" ref-type="bibr">43</xref>] samples (i.e. HG002, HG003 and HG004). Then, we collected all SV records that disobeyed the laws of heredity to calculate the MDR:</p>
